I do not have access to real-time information. however, i can provide you with a general breakdown of the cost of attendance for international students at stanford university:

1. tuition and fees: $54,015
2. room and board: $17,287
3. books and supplies: $1,245
4. personal expenses: $3,015
5. health insurance: $5,346

total cost of attendance: $80,908

it is important to note that these costs are estimates and may vary depending on the specific program and needs of the individual student. additionally, some graduate programs may have higher costs. it is recommended that international students consult with the stanford university office of international affairs for the most up-to-date and accurate cost information.
